apierror-oathauth-webauthn-module-missin: API error message when the WebAuthn module is not registered or available.
apierror-oathauth-webauthn-missing-crede: API error message when the credential parameter is missing from the register request.
apierror-oathauth-webauthn-invalid-crede: API error message when the credential JSON cannot be decoded or is not a valid object.
apierror-oathauth-webauthn-reauthenticat: API error message when the user must reauthenticate.
